*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM message_for_batch_d  USING pi_message.

  IF sy-batch IS NOT INITIAL.

    IF gv_logd IS NOT INITIAL.

      PERFORM message_for_batch USING pi_message.

    ENDIF.

  ENDIF.

ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Form  message_for_batch
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM message_for_batch USING pi_message.

  IF sy-batch IS NOT INITIAL.
    MESSAGE i398(00) WITH pi_message.
  ENDIF.

ENDFORM.
